  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Let's use this issue to consolidate all the RANDAO related design spec and issues. Vitalik has put out an [outline](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/33) in the [latest beacon chain spec](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/master/specs/beacon-chain.md) for implementers to follow.\r\n\r\nHighlevel-view, looking at the spec, we'll need to make the following changes to support RANDAO:\r\n- On start up, add validator and their randao commitment\r\n- Add new field randao mix in active state\r\n- Verify randao, proposer index, and peel off the next randao hash onion commitment for the assigned proposer during attestation processing \r\n- Update Active state with the new randao\r\n- Reshuffle validator set with the randao commitment during state recalculation\r\n",
